Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.81,0:00:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  都说不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.52,0:00:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咯吱咯吱  咯吱咯吱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.97,0:00:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快停手  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  悠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.60,0:00:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  天女目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不…来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是小一的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.35,0:00:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她把它落在游泳池边了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.49,0:00:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  谢谢你哦  我去交给她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天女目你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.34,0:00:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是渚同学的…姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
